      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of character? This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready for a new owner who appreciates a solid, functional car that's been driven and enjoyed. It\u2019s a great opportunity to get into a quality model at a more accessible price point, offering a reliable driving experience with some room for your own personal touches!",
