    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's perfect for your daily commute! This well-loved vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter, offering a solid driving experience at a great value. While it shows some honest signs of use and minor cosmetic wear, it remains a reliable and practical choice for anyone looking for functional transportation without the high price tag. Come see why this honest, hard-working car is the right fit for you!",
