      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is in great shape with only slight wear on the driver's side bolster. Mechanically, the car is solid, with all features and electronics functioning as intended and a consistent service history. It offers a great balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal for a buyer looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated mechanic or someone looking for a parts donor. The engine is difficult to start and runs roughly, often stalling at stops, and the transmission exhibits significant slipping. Cosmetically, the body shows heavy rust and clear coat failure, while the interior has multiple tears and non-functional electronics. Expect to invest significant time and resources to make this car roadworthy again.",
